Cross platform game development framework

- Our mission
   - Best framework for development of mobile games.

- Platforms
   - iOS
   - Android 
   - Windows
   - Mac OS X

Enhancing dava framework
https://github.com/dava/dava.framework/wiki/Topics-that-requires-investigation

- Why not other's
   - Cocos 2D. It's a great technology but it's hardly portable
   - Unity. It's a great technology but it's not free, and you can't modify or improve it. 
   - UDK. It's a great engine, but again it's not free, and you can't modify or improve it. 
